The method updateSearchItemQA starts by checking whether questiond and answer are computed in
            if (mQa != null) {
                return;
            }

If it is already computed, then it will not compute it again. So the function called immediately returns. Does it answer your question ? I would expect "content" to be the caller, but I expect your question being about the function which is called, so it's not clear to me here what it means.

